{"serial": "61002", "department_serial": 55, "code": "AP1006", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Vector Analysis", "ch": "向量分析"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liou, Yu-Chieng"], "ch": ["廖宇慶"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "S1", "room": "625"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "大氣科學學系", "en": "Department of Atmospheric Physics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 49, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "建立以向量描述自然界物理量的觀念，熟練向量運算，並能夠靈活應用各種定理。本課程為各位日後修習力學、電磁學、流體力學、大氣動力學等重要課程的基礎。", "en": "“The goal of this class is to establish the students‘ capability in using vector to describe physical quantities and laws. Students need to learn basic computations, and is able to apply the concept of vector to solve problems according to their purpose. Vector analysis is the basic class for future advanced courses in this department such as Mechanics, Electricity and Magnetism, Fluid Mechanics, as well as Atmospheric Dynamics.“"}, "outline": {"ch": "教學大綱：\n(1)向量的基本運算。\n(2)Tensor notation。\n(3)位置、速度(Velocity)、加速度(Acceleration)。\n(4)曲率(Curvature)和扭率(Torsion)。\n(5)梯度(Gradient)、輻合/輻散(Convergence/Divergence)、旋度(Curl)。\n(6)線積分與面積分。\n(7)格林定理(Green’s theorem)、位勢定理(Potential theory)。\n(8)高斯輻合輻散定理 (Gauss theorem)、斯托克定理(Stokes’s theorem)。\n(9)曲線(直角)座標系統(Curvilinear coordinates)。\n教學目標：\n   建立以向量描述自然界物理量的觀念。熟練向量的運算，並能夠靈活應用各種定理。本課程為各位日後修習力學、電磁學、流體力學、大氣動力學等重要課程的基礎。", "en": "教學大綱：\n(1)basic laws in vector computation.\n(2)Tensor notation。\n(3)位置、速度(Velocity)、加速度(Acceleration)。\n(4)曲率(Curvature)和扭率(Torsion)。\n(5)梯度(Gradient)、輻合/輻散(Convergence/Divergence)、旋度(Curl)。\n(6)線積分與面積分。\n(7)格林定理(Green’s theorem)、位勢定理(Potential theory)。\n(8)高斯輻合輻散定理 (Gauss theorem)、斯托克定理(Stokes’s theorem)。\n(9)曲線(直角)座標系統(Curvilinear coordinates)。\n教學目標：\n   建立以向量描述自然界物理量的觀念。熟練向量的運算，並能夠靈活應用各種定理。本課程為各位日後修習力學、電磁學、流體力學、大氣動力學等重要課程的基礎。"}, "textbook": {"ch": "參考書目：\nAdvanced Engineering Mathematics.           P. V. O’Neil.\n推薦課外科普讀物:\n費瑪最後定理 (臺灣商務)\n尋找地球刻度的人(時報)\n肝炎聖戰(天下文化)\n毛起來說e (天下文化)\n毛起來說三角(天下文化)\n洞察(天下文化)\n微塵大千(天下文化)\n吳健雄傳-物理科學的第一夫人(時報)\n規範與對稱之美- 楊振寧傳(天下文化)\n上班族的諾貝爾奇蹟 (遠流)", "en": "參考書目：\nAdvanced Engineering Mathematics.           P. V. O’Neil.\n推薦課外科普讀物:\n費瑪最後定理 (臺灣商務)\n尋找地球刻度的人(時報)\n肝炎聖戰(天下文化)\n毛起來說e (天下文化)\n毛起來說三角(天下文化)\n洞察(天下文化)\n微塵大千(天下文化)\n吳健雄傳-物理科學的第一夫人(時報)\n規範與對稱之美- 楊振寧傳(天下文化)\n上班族的諾貝爾奇蹟 (遠流)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "考試（90％）\n出席率(10％；出席率至少一半以上才開始算分)", "en": "Exam（90％）\nAttendance(10％；出席率至少一半以上才開始算分)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "Any time !", "en": "Any  time !"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "基礎學科(共同)", "en": "基礎學科(共同)"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "數理基礎能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "專業知識能力", "rating": "(2)低", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "資訊應用能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野與語文溝通能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理及服務學習之能力", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Ability in basic mathematics and science", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in professional knowledge", "rating": "(2)Low", "assesments": ["Test/Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in information applications", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in international horizons and communication", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Ability in independent thinking", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Test/Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Abil